title: SEC requests restraining order to temporarily freeze Binance.US assets
description:
The U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) filed a motion requesting a restraining order against Binance.US on June 6. That request specifically asks the court to freeze the assets of Binance.US’s parent companies, which are collectively operating under the name BAM. The SEC’s motion also seeks to have Binance.US funds returned to customers alongside other […]
